		y: -2.0d
		dependencies: ["000000000000E01B"]
		title: "Chalk the Circle"
		icon: {id: "occultism:chalk_white", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Rituals in Occultism require chalk circles drawn on the ground. White Chalk is the base. Draw the ritual pattern from the Occultism book (the Dictionary of Spirits), place the required items at the focal points, and activate.", "The chalk is consumed. The circle is temporary. The demon it calls is not."]
		tasks: [{
